Subject: [PATCH 028/111] Add support for RAM size detection

DDR size on UCM-iMX8M-Mini rev.1.1 is hardwired and must be read via GPIOs.
Possible values are:
+----------+-----------+-----------------+
| GPIO 1:0 | GPIO 1:15 | RAM SIZE in GiB |
+----------+-----------+-----------------+
| 0        | 0         | 1               |
| 1        | 0         | 4               |
| 1        | 1         | 2               |
| 0        | 1         | unallowed       |
+----------+-----------+-----------------+

